# Archived run reports land here, one folder per run:
#   run-reports/history/<short-sha>-<timestamp>/
#     ├── latest.json
#     ├── latest.md
#     └── console-latest.log (if captured)
# The current run stays at run-reports/latest.*. Previous run is moved to
# history by scripts/run-report.js before the new one is written.
